caption: "Electronic cannabis delivery system"
created: 20260405120000000
modified: 20260405120000000
title: Policy1331(s1)(3)
type: text/vnd.tiddlywiki

shall mean an electronic device that may be used to simulate smoking in the delivery of cannabis to a person inhaling the device and includes, but is not limited to, a vaporizer, electronic pipe, electronic hookah and any related device and any cartridge or other component of such device.
